# Week of January 1, 2024

## Deactivated

Remove deactivated NPIs with no reactivation date




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
wk_2024_01_01_deact <- wk_2024_01_01$basic |> 
  filter(!is.na(deact_date), is.na(react_date)) |> 
  remove_quiet()

wk_2024_01_01_deact_npi <- sf_convert(uniq_narm(wk_2024_01_01_deact$npi))

length(wk_2024_01_01_deact_npi)
```

## Address

Filter out deactivated NPIs




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
wk_2024_01_01_address <- wk_2024_01_01$address |> 
  filter(!npi %in% wk_2024_01_01_deact_npi) |> 
  select(
    npi,
    ends_with("address"),
    ends_with("city"),
    ends_with("state"),
    ends_with("zip"),
    ends_with("country"),
    ends_with("phone"),
    ends_with("fax"))
```
:::




Exact match on all address fields




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
exact <- wk_2024_01_01_address |> 
  filter(
    mail_address == prac_address,
    mail_city == prac_city,
    mail_state == prac_state,
    mail_zip == prac_zip,
    mail_country == prac_country,
    mail_phone == prac_phone,
    mail_fax == prac_fax
    ) |> 
  select(-starts_with("prac_")) |> 
  mutate(type = "Both") |>
  reframe(
    npi,
    type,
    address = mail_address,
    city = mail_city,
    state = mail_state,
    zip = mail_zip,
    country = mail_country,
    phone = mail_phone,
    fax = mail_fax)
```
:::




Match on all fields except fax




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
fax <- wk_2024_01_01_address |>             
  filter(
    !npi %in% exact$npi,        
         mail_address == prac_address, 
         mail_city == prac_city,
         mail_state == prac_state,
         mail_country == prac_country,
         mail_zip == prac_zip,
         mail_phone == prac_phone) |> 
  reframe(
    npi,
    type = "Both",
    address = mail_address,
    city = mail_city,
    state = mail_state,
    zip = mail_zip,
    country = mail_country,
    phone = mail_phone,
    fax = case_when(
      !is.na(mail_fax) & !is.na(prac_fax) & mail_fax == prac_fax ~ str_glue("M: {mail_fax}"),
      !is.na(mail_fax) & !is.na(prac_fax) & mail_fax != prac_fax ~ str_glue("M: {mail_fax} | P: {prac_fax}"),
      !is.na(mail_fax) & is.na(prac_fax) ~ str_glue("M: {mail_fax}"),
      is.na(mail_fax) & !is.na(prac_fax) ~ str_glue("P: {prac_fax}"),
      .default = NA_character_))
```
:::




Match on all fields except zip, phone, and fax




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
zipphonefax <- wk_2024_01_01_address |>             
  filter(!npi %in% c(exact$npi, fax$npi),        
         mail_address == prac_address,
         mail_city == prac_city,
         mail_state == prac_state,
         mail_country == prac_country) |>
  reframe(
    npi,
    type = "Both",
    address = mail_address,
    city = mail_city,
    state = mail_state,
    country = mail_country,
    zip = case_when(
      !is.na(mail_zip) & !is.na(prac_zip) & mail_zip == prac_zip ~ str_glue("M: {mail_zip}"),
      !is.na(mail_zip) & !is.na(prac_zip) & mail_zip != prac_zip ~ str_glue("M: {mail_zip} | P: {prac_zip}"),
      !is.na(mail_zip) & is.na(prac_zip) ~ str_glue("M: {mail_zip}"),
      is.na(mail_zip) & !is.na(prac_zip) ~ str_glue("P: {prac_zip}"),
      .default = NA_character_),
    phone = case_when(
      !is.na(mail_phone) & !is.na(prac_phone) & mail_phone == prac_phone ~ str_glue("M: {mail_phone}"),
      !is.na(mail_phone) & !is.na(prac_phone) & mail_phone != prac_phone ~ str_glue("M: {mail_phone} | P: {prac_phone}"),
      !is.na(mail_phone) & is.na(prac_phone) ~ str_glue("M: {mail_phone}"),
      is.na(mail_phone) & !is.na(prac_phone) ~ str_glue("P: {prac_phone}"),
      .default = NA_character_),
    fax = case_when(
      !is.na(mail_fax) & !is.na(prac_fax) & mail_fax == prac_fax ~ str_glue("M: {mail_fax}"),
      !is.na(mail_fax) & !is.na(prac_fax) & mail_fax != prac_fax ~ str_glue("M: {mail_fax} | P: {prac_fax}"),
      !is.na(mail_fax) & is.na(prac_fax) ~ str_glue("M: {mail_fax}"),
      is.na(mail_fax) & !is.na(prac_fax) ~ str_glue("P: {prac_fax}"),
      .default = NA_character_)
    )
```
:::




Pivot remaining addresses




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
pivot <- wk_2024_01_01_address |> 
  filter(!npi %in% c(exact$npi, fax$npi, zipphonefax$npi)) |> 
  pivot_longer(
    -npi, 
    names_to = "type_part", 
    values_to = "value", 
    names_transform = list(type_part = stringr::str_to_title)) |> 
  separate_wider_delim(
    type_part, 
    delim = "_", 
    names = c("type", "part")) |> 
  pivot_wider(names_from = part, values_from = value)
```
:::




Combine all address matches




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
wk_2024_01_01_address_clean <- vctrs::vec_rbind(
  exact, 
  fax, 
  zipphonefax, 
  pivot) |> 
  left_join(wk_2024_01_01_basic[c("npi", "entity")], by = join_by(npi))

wk_2024_01_01_address_clean |> filter(entity == "Ind")
```
